  "remarks": "Deputy Prosecutor General. In 2007–2008, he opened cases against independent media, journalists and opposition parties. He authorised searches by the KGB officers of the premises of \"Radio Racyja\",  \"ERB\" television \"Belsat\", in the Grodno office of the Belarusian Popular Front and the NGO \"Batskavshchyna\", as well the apartments of 17 journalists.",
